1. *Prljavi* tanjir neću da stavim u čistu mašinu za sudove. (I won't put the *dirty* plate in the clean dishwasher.)
2. Da li si video koliko *prljav* prozor imaju ti susedi? (Have you seen how *dirty* the window of those neighbors is?)
3. Oni su *prljavi* igrači i uvek varaju. (They are *dirty* players and always cheat.)
4. *Prljavim* rukama ne diraj hranu! (Don't touch food with *dirty* hands!)
5. Ova soba je stvarno *prljava*, moramo da je očistimo. (This room is really *dirty*, we need to clean it.)
6. Ne volim da čistim *prljavu* sudoperu. (I don't like cleaning the *dirty* sink.)
7. *Prljave* čarape bacam u veš mašinu nakon jednog nošenja. (I put *dirty* socks in the washing machine after wearing them once.)
8. Nemoj da bacaš smeće na ulici, to je *prljavo* i nekulturno. (Don't litter on the street, it's *dirty* and uncivilized.)
9. On je *prljav* igrač i ne poštuje pravila. (He is a *dirty* player and doesn't respect the rules.)
10. Stavi pečurke u *prljavi* tanjir, ne u ovaj čist. (Put the mushrooms on the *dirty* plate, not on this clean one.)